---
// src/pages/reviews/m5-max-macbook-pro-review.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="M5 Max MacBook Pro Review 2026 - Fastest Apple Chip Ever"
  description="Read our M5 Max MacBook Pro review. The fastest Apple chip ever with 29,233 multi-core performance. Complete specs and buying guide."
  article={true}
  publishedTime="2026-03-06"
  author="ReviewCloud"
>
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Laptops</span>
      <h1>M5 Max MacBook Pro Review: The Fastest Apple Chip Ever</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud Team</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="rating">
      <span class="score">5.0</span>
      <span class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
    </div>

    <div class="price-banner">
      <span class="price">Starting at $2,499</span>
      <span class="release">Launch: March 11, 2026</span>
    </div>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#performance">Performance</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">New Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#verdict">Verdict</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <section id="overview">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The <strong>MacBook Pro with M5 Max</strong> is the most powerful laptop Apple has ever created. Featuring the new M5 Max chip, it delivers groundbreaking performance for professionals.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="performance">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <p>The M5 Max sets new records in every benchmark category:</p>
      <div class="benchmark-table">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Device</th>
              <th>Multi-Core</th>
              <th>Single-Core</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>MacBook Pro M5 Max (18-core)</td>
              <td>29,233</td>
              <td>4,268</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Mac Studio M3 Ultra</td>
              <td>27,726</td>
              <td>~3,200</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>MacBook Pro M4 Max</td>
              <td>25,702</td>
              <td>~3,800</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>The M5 Max is up to <strong>15% faster</strong> CPU and <strong>20% faster</strong> GPU than M4 Max. It even tops every other consumer PC processor in the Geekbench database.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
      <h2>New Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>18-core CPU with up to 40-core GPU</li>
        <li>Unified memory up to 256GB</li>
        <li>Neural Engine for AI workloads</li>
        <li>Enhanced media engine for 8K video editing</li>
        <li>All-day battery life</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="verdict">
      <h2>Verdict</h2>
      <p>The M5 Max MacBook Pro is perfect for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Professional video editors</li>
        <li>3D artists and animators</li>
        <li>Software developers</li>
        <li>AI/ML researchers</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="buy-links">
        <h3>Where to Buy</h3>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=MacBook+Pro+M5&tag=rc0440-20" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
          Pre-order on Amazon
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: white; }
  .review-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .category { background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .review-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .meta { color: #666; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .rating { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .score { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #667eea; }
  .stars { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-left: 1rem; }
  .price-banner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; background: #e8f5e9; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .price { font-weight: 700; color: #2e7d32; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .release { color: #666; }
  .toc { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .toc h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .toc ul { list-style: none; }
  .toc li { padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .toc a { color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  section h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  section p { color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .benchmark-table { overflow-x: auto; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
  th { background: #667eea; color: white; }
  tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f8f9fa; }
  ul { margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #555; }
  .buy-links { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .buy-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #ff9900; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
  .buy-links { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .buy-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #ff9900; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .buy-btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
</style>
